questions.subject: ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace
questions.question: How does the ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace extension implement multiple workspaces?
questions.answer: It provides 5 quick workspace slots to work with flows.

questions.subject: ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace
questions.question: What is the planned future of the ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace extension?
questions.answer: The developer aims to automate the workspace selection and update process based on the flow.

questions.subject: ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace
questions.question: What additional features would enhance the ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace extension?
questions.answer: The developer suggests creating custom nodes to allow workspaces to be part of the workspace hierarchy.

questions.subject: ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace
questions.question: Where can I find a video demonstrating the implementation of multiple workspaces in ComfyUI?
questions.answer: The developer has uploaded a video to YouTube showcasing the extension's functionality.
